com.microfocus.adm.pulse.pluginapi.event

Interface PulseChainFinishedEventListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable, PulseChainEventPlugin, PulseEventPlugin, PulsePlugin

    public interface PulseChainFinishedEventListener
extends PulseChainEventPlugin

    Plugins that implement this interface will receive a notification when a chain finishes.

    See also PulseChainStartedEventListener and PulseChainQueuedEventListener.

    Since:
    19.1.1
